overview: Ana Foxxx and Sarah Banks are nurses, sharing a private moment between rounds. Ana returns later in the movie as a bartender dealing with a rowdy patron, who gets some comfort from waitress Jenna Foxx. Skyler Nicole and Chanell Heart meet up for a quickie after Chanell's husband leaves for work, and Anya Ivy gives Daya Knight the massage of her dreams.
title: Lesbian Beauties 19: All Black Beauties
